Kuoni Has Resources for Asia Purchases, Rothwell Tells Finanz

-- B y   G i l e s   B r o o m
-- 
2011-09-23T17:09:59Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-23/kuoni-has-resources-for-asia-purchases-rothwell-tells-finanz.html
Kuoni Reisen Holding AG (KUNN) ’s financial
resources are reserved mainly for acquisitions in  Asia , Finanz &
Wirtschaft reported, citing an interview with Chief Executive
Officer Peter Rothwell.  The company expects to see little growth in  Europe  and has
“problems” in Italy and  Spain , Rothwell was cited as saying in
a pre-release of a story that will be published in the newspaper
tomorrow.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Giles Broom in Geneva at   gbroom@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Frank Connelly in Paris at 
